{"type":"message","id":"2b39b53a","parentId":"1ab33420","timestamp":"2026-04-06T01:32:40.966Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9ks0sjrFnrvINDnZBxYQxJ4V","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: okx market <action> [args...]\n\nMarket data (ticker, orderbook, candles, trades).\n\nCommands:\n  ticker           Get latest ticker data for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market ticker <instId>\n\n  tickers          Get all tickers for an instrument type (SPOT|SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION)\n                   Usage: okx market tickers <instType>\n\n  orderbook        Get order book depth for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market orderbook <instId> [--sz <n>]\n\n  candles          Get candlestick (OHLCV) data\n                   Usage: okx market candles <instId> [--bar <bar>] [--limit <n>]\n\n  instruments      List tradable instruments of a given type\n                   Usage: okx market instruments --instType <type> [--instId <id>]\n\n  funding-rate     Get current or historical funding rate for perpetual swaps\n                   Usage: okx market funding-rate <instId> [--history] [--limit <n>]\n\n  mark-price       Get mark price for instruments\n                   Usage: okx market mark-price --instType <MARGIN|SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION> [--instId <id>]\n\n  trades           Get recent trades for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market trades <instId> [--limit <n>]\n\n  index-ticker     Get index ticker data\n                   Usage: okx market index-ticker [--instId <id>] [--quoteCcy <ccy>]\n\n  index-candles    Get index candlestick data\n                   Usage: okx market index-candles <instId> [--bar <bar>] [--limit <n>] [--history]\n\n  price-limit      Get price limit for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market price-limit <instId>\n\n  open-interest    Get open interest for instruments\n                   Usage: okx market open-interest --instType <SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION> [--instId <id>]\n\n  stock-tokens     List all stock token instruments (instCategory=3, e.g. AAPL-USDT-SWAP)\n                   Usage: okx market stock-tokens [--instType <SPOT|SWAP>] [--instId <id>]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5516,"aggregated":"Usage: okx market <action> [args...]\n\nMarket data (ticker, orderbook, candles, trades).\n\nCommands:\n  ticker           Get latest ticker data for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market ticker <instId>\n\n  tickers          Get all tickers for an instrument type (SPOT|SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION)\n                   Usage: okx market tickers <instType>\n\n  orderbook        Get order book depth for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market orderbook <instId> [--sz <n>]\n\n  candles          Get candlestick (OHLCV) data\n                   Usage: okx market candles <instId> [--bar <bar>] [--limit <n>]\n\n  instruments      List tradable instruments of a given type\n                   Usage: okx market instruments --instType <type> [--instId <id>]\n\n  funding-rate     Get current or historical funding rate for perpetual swaps\n                   Usage: okx market funding-rate <instId> [--history] [--limit <n>]\n\n  mark-price       Get mark price for instruments\n                   Usage: okx market mark-price --instType <MARGIN|SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION> [--instId <id>]\n\n  trades           Get recent trades for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market trades <instId> [--limit <n>]\n\n  index-ticker     Get index ticker data\n                   Usage: okx market index-ticker [--instId <id>] [--quoteCcy <ccy>]\n\n  index-candles    Get index candlestick data\n                   Usage: okx market index-candles <instId> [--bar <bar>] [--limit <n>] [--history]\n\n  price-limit      Get price limit for an instrument\n                   Usage: okx market price-limit <instId>\n\n  open-interest    Get open interest for instruments\n                   Usage: okx market open-interest --instType <SWAP|FUTURES|OPTION> [--instId <id>]\n\n  stock-tokens     List all stock token instruments (instCategory=3, e.g. AAPL-USDT-SWAP)\n                   Usage: okx market stock-tokens [--instType <SPOT|SWAP>] [--instId <id>]","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775439160963}}
