{"type":"message","id":"17188c30","parentId":"41b760b0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:15:35.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Firsr0iEfOzJmSCHenAPYibu","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Search: Bitcoin ETF flows latest farside site:farside.co.uk OR site:bitbo.io\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nBitcoin ETF flows show significant inflows and outflows, with notable activity in January 2024. Latest data indicates substantial inflows in January 2026. Farside Investors provides real-time updates on Bitcoin ETF flows.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m) – Farside Investors** (87%)\n  https://www.farside.co.uk/bitcoin-etf-flow\n  Title: Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m) – Farside Investors\n| Farside  * Fund * ETF Flows   + Bitcoin   + Ethereum   + Solana * Basis * Books * About * Login |. # Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m). | Date | IBIT | FBTC | BITB | ARKB | BTCO | EZBC | BRRR | HODL | BTCW | GBTC | BTC | Total |. | 11 Jan 2024 | 111.7 | 227.0 | 237.9 | 65.3 | 17.4 | 50.1 | 29.4 | 10.6 | 1.0 | (95.1) | - | 655.3 |. | ...\n\n- **Bitcoin ETF Flow (US$m) – Farside Investors** (86%)\n  https://farside.co.uk/btc?from=article-links\n  Title: Bitcoin ETF Flow (US$m) – Farside Investors\n| Farside  * Fund * ETF Flows   + Bitcoin   + Ethereum   + Solana * Basis * Books * About * Login |. # Bitcoin ETF Flow (US$m). |  | Blackrock | Fidelity | Bitwise | Ark | Invesco | Franklin | Valkyrie | VanEck | WTree | Grayscale | Grayscale | Total |. |  | IBIT | FBTC | BITB | ARKB | BTCO | EZBC | BRRR | HODL | BTCW | GBTC | BTC |  |. | Fee | 0....\n\n- **Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m) – Farside Investors** (85%)\n  https://farside.co.uk/bitcoin-etf-flow-all-data#site-content\n  Title: Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m) – Farside Investors\n| Farside  * Fund * ETF Flows   + Bitcoin   + Ethereum   + Solana * Basis * Books * About * Login |. # Bitcoin ETF Flow – All Data (US$m). | Date | IBIT | FBTC | BITB | ARKB